Introduction

Jo is a Japanese singer and dancer under HYBE Labels Japan. He is best known as the lead vocalist, visual and center of the Japanese boy group &TEAM.

In 2022, Jo participated in the survival show "&AUDITION - The Howling -" where he qualified to become a member of the Japanese boy group &TEAM.
